{"tid":91423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】黃興國涉受賄","createTime":"2017-01-22T23:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T02:36:49.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"71a9f349bd24ad4d5101e297cc87f339e10a4a4c","tid":91423,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T23:57:37.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】中國最高檢官網22日上午發布消息指，最高人民檢察院日前經審查決定，依法對天津市委原代理書記、原市長黃興國以涉嫌受賄罪立案偵查並採取強制措施。案件偵查工作正在進行中。<br />\n　　黃興國是浙江人，1954年出生，曾長期在浙江工作，有傳他是原中共政治局常委黃菊的侄子。2003年，黃興國從寧波市委書記調任天津市副市長，2008年起任天津市長，2014年低，因令計劃案發，原天津市委書記孫春蘭調任中共統戰部長，黃興國就開始了代理天津市委書記。<br />\n　　2015年8月12日，天津港發生大爆炸，引致160多人喪生，黃興國在之後的新聞發布會上稱，自己對大爆炸「負有不可推卸責任」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5122c32dc132a2b9b75e9dd3c7678e944909e2c","tid":91423,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:01:05.000Z","msg":"睇錯"},{"pid":"e8739e1beaf31e3ecef6b9fd404c7601a9c8bb0a","tid":91423,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:07:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯</blockquote><br />\n樓主就係想你睇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86797992a3720b9be22b5a50eb39c69b6aeaaa8d","tid":91423,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:10:54.000Z","msg":"失望"},{"pid":"b87ea26324b0f646d13f08fa05cc9ecfba051c11","tid":91423,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:11:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌中伏"},{"pid":"347e6e2277a865d323d914afc5297d6db160e1f3","tid":91423,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T00:28:39.000Z","msg":"等我仲咁興奮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p